This holistic ethos is supported by a growing body of evidence. Research from institutions like Harvard Medical School and the Mayo Clinic underscores the benefits of integrative medicine, showing improved patient outcomes in areas such as cardiovascular health, immune function, and emotional well-being. At MedNova+, we've seen firsthand how this approach leads to profound transformations: clients report reduced reliance on medications, increased energy levels, stronger relationships, and a renewed sense of purpose.
